{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, we have utilized predictive models based on Naive Bayes and Logistic Regression.",
    "These models generate the probability of a class variable attaining a specific value, which signifies either success or failure in our case.",
    "The NBC model calculates the likelihood of a particular outcome for a class variable, such as success or failure.",
    "Bayesian Networks provide a variety of probabilitybased classifiers (Kotsiantis et al. 2006).",
    "Among these, the Naive Bayes Classifier (NBC) stands out due to its simplicity and effectiveness (Berrar 2018)."
  ]
}